WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:03.174
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:03.174 --> 00:04.715
I WAS ABLE TO TRACE
THIS PHOTOGRAPH BACK TO YOU.

00:04.715 --> 00:06.087
EMILY WILL DO ANYTHING
FOR DAVID,

00:06.087 --> 00:08.179
INCLUDING ERASING
HIS DEBTS.

00:08.179 --> 00:10.010
WHICH MIGHT PROVE INTERESTING
TO YOUR EMPLOYER.

00:15.226 --> 00:16.227
MY FATHER LIED.

00:16.227 --> 00:17.808
CONRAD DIDN'T
HOLD HIM CAPTIVE.

00:17.808 --> 00:19.270
IT WAS A MAN
NAMED MALCOLM BLACK.

00:19.270 --> 00:21.142
I BELIEVE THAT KATE
IS HIS OPERATIVE.

00:21.142 --> 00:21.982
I'M PREGNANT.

00:21.982 --> 00:23.194
DANIEL LOVES YOU.

00:23.194 --> 00:25.025
BUT WHAT IF
I DON'T LOVE HIM ANYMORE?

00:25.025 --> 00:27.027
YOUR TEARS
SUGGEST OTHERWISE.

00:27.027 --> 00:28.109
PLEASE, DANIEL,
COME HOME.

00:28.109 --> 00:29.240
I NEED YOU.
 WE NEED YOU.

00:29.990 --> 00:31.242
MALCOLM'S MY FATHER.

00:31.242 --> 00:33.074
YOUR COVER IS BLOWN.
 [ GUN CLICKS ]

00:33.074 --> 00:33.954
[ SCREAMS ]

00:35.536 --> 00:36.457
[ EMILY GRUNTING ]

00:36.457 --> 00:37.658
EMILY!
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

00:37.658 --> 00:38.579
GET OUT OF HERE!
RUN!

00:39.290 --> 00:40.831
NO!

00:41.962 --> 00:43.084
DROP IT!

00:44.295 --> 00:45.426
YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY,
DANIEL.

00:45.426 --> 00:47.007
YOU'RE STILL LYING
TO ME.

00:52.133 --> 00:54.225
[ GUNSHOTS ]

00:57.268 --> 00:58.679
WAS THAT...

00:58.679 --> 01:01.642
THAT WAS GUNSHOTS.

01:01.642 --> 01:05.065
I WANT TO REPORT THAT I JUST
HEARD GUNSHOTS AT GRAYSON MANOR.

01:22.543 --> 01:24.505
AMANDA, WHAT HAPPENED?

01:29.170 --> 01:31.302
DANIEL!

01:31.302 --> 01:33.764
NO! DANIEL!

01:33.764 --> 01:35.136
DANIEL!

01:35.136 --> 01:37.178
[ SOBBING ]

01:37.178 --> 01:39.600
OH, GOD!
WHAT DID YOU DO?!

01:43.724 --> 01:45.686
HE WASN'T SUPPOSED
TO BE HERE.

01:45.686 --> 01:46.397
YOU HURT?

01:46.397 --> 01:48.319
HOLD MY HAND. DON'T LET GO.

01:49.190 --> 01:51.192
[ INHALES DEEPLY, GRUNTS ]

01:51.192 --> 01:51.992
[ SHOULDER POPS ]

01:51.992 --> 01:54.695
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

01:59.410 --> 02:02.163
[ SOBBING ]

02:03.664 --> 02:06.457
CHIEF. IS IT TRUE?
SHOTS FIRED AT GRAYSON MANOR?

02:06.457 --> 02:09.049
I'M TAKING TWO UNITS
OUT THERE RIGHT NOW.

02:09.049 --> 02:11.172
I'M COMING.
 ISN'T YOUR SHIFT OVER?

02:11.172 --> 02:13.844
EMILY THORNE'S A FRIEND.
I'M CLOCKING BACK IN.

02:13.844 --> 02:16.136
WHERE'S THE AMBULANCE?

02:16.136 --> 02:18.058
WHAT'S TAKING SO LONG?

02:18.058 --> 02:19.059
WE CALLED.

02:19.059 --> 02:21.182
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
SHE'S NOT AN FBI AGENT?

02:21.182 --> 02:22.523
NO, SHE WAS
A REAL FBI AGENT --

02:22.523 --> 02:24.435
WHO WAS ALSO MOONLIGHTING
FOR MALCOLM BLACK.

02:25.526 --> 02:27.027
YOU WERE SUPPOSED
TO STAY OUT OF THIS.

02:27.027 --> 02:28.068
AND YOU'RE MISSING
THE POINT.

02:28.068 --> 02:30.571
SHE WASN'T JUST WORKING FOR HIM.
SHE WAS HIS DAUGHTER.

02:33.484 --> 02:35.826
AND SHE KNEW WHO YOU WERE?

02:35.826 --> 02:37.618
I DON'T KNOW HOW,
BUT SHE DID.

02:38.699 --> 02:41.452
SHE WANTED THE MONEY
THAT YOU TOOK.

02:41.452 --> 02:42.833
SHE WAS COMING
FOR YOU NEXT.

02:44.084 --> 02:45.746
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

02:48.168 --> 02:50.170
[ VIBRATING CONTINUES ]

02:56.677 --> 02:59.099
"EXPECTED TO HEAR FROM YOU.
WHERE ARE YOU?

02:59.099 --> 03:00.301
CHECK IN NOW,
OR I GET INVOLVED."

03:01.181 --> 03:02.973
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'VE JUST DONE.

03:02.973 --> 03:03.974
WHAT I'VE DONE?

03:03.974 --> 03:05.476
SHE -- SHE TRIED TO KILL ME.

03:05.476 --> 03:06.857
OH, SHE DID KILL YOU.

03:06.857 --> 03:09.149
SHE KILLED ALL OF US.
YOU JUST DON'T KNOW IT YET.

03:09.149 --> 03:10.941
[ SIGHS ]

03:10.941 --> 03:12.403
YOU KNOW WHAT
THIS MAN'S CAPABLE OF?

03:12.403 --> 03:13.864
YEARS AGO, HIS NEPHEW
WAS IN A CAR ACCIDENT.

03:13.864 --> 03:15.115
HE WAS CRIPPLED.

03:15.115 --> 03:17.197
A WEEK LATER,
THE DRUNK DRIVER DISAPPEARED,

03:17.197 --> 03:19.119
ALONG WITH HIS WIFE,
HIS PARENTS, HIS CHILDREN,

03:19.119 --> 03:20.371
AND HIS BROTHER.

03:20.371 --> 03:23.494
THEIR BODIES WERE FOUND
IN A HUNTING SHACK.

03:23.494 --> 03:24.875
THEY'D BEEN TORTURED
FOR SIX WEEKS.

03:24.875 --> 03:26.877
IF HE FINDS OUT
THAT YOU KILLED HIS DAUGHTER --

03:26.877 --> 03:28.168
IT WAS ME.

03:28.168 --> 03:30.000
IT DOESN'T MATTER.
HE'LL BURY US ALL.

03:33.093 --> 03:34.715
THEN WE HAVE TO MAKE SURE
HE DOESN'T FIND OUT.

03:39.970 --> 03:41.051
♪ TAKE A SIT ♪

03:41.051 --> 03:42.843
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

03:42.843 --> 03:44.515
♪ TAKE SOME TIME TO ♪

03:44.515 --> 03:48.649
DANIEL, I HOPE YOU HAVEN'T HAD
DESSERT, BECAUSE I'M JUST AB--

03:48.649 --> 03:52.192
OH, SIMONE. PARDON,
I THOUGHT YOU WERE --

03:52.192 --> 03:55.195
NO. NO. WHY WOULD
THE NEWS DESK CALL?

03:58.198 --> 04:00.200
WAIT.

04:00.200 --> 04:02.122
WAIT, WHAT DID THEY SAY?

04:10.000 --> 04:12.463
[ CELLPHONE CLATTERS ]

04:12.463 --> 04:15.215
[ CRYING ]

04:15.215 --> 04:18.007
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

04:29.560 --> 04:32.733
ARE YOU OKAY TO CONTINUE,
MISS THORNE? YOU SEEM...

04:32.733 --> 04:34.855
NO, I'M -- I'M OKAY.

04:34.855 --> 04:37.157
SO, YOU WERE HOME
FROM THE PARTY MAYBE AN HOUR

04:37.157 --> 04:39.239
WHEN MR. GRAYSON STARTED
KNOCKING ON YOUR DOOR?

04:39.239 --> 04:42.112
UH, HE WAS POUNDING ON IT.
[ SIGHS ] YELLING.

04:42.112 --> 04:43.744
WHAT WAS HE YELLING?

04:43.744 --> 04:44.955
TO LET HIM IN,

04:44.955 --> 04:47.748
THAT I RUINED HIS LIFE.

04:47.748 --> 04:50.080
HE WAS, UH --

04:50.080 --> 04:52.002
HE WAS REALLY ANGRY --

04:52.002 --> 04:55.295
DRUNK, MAYBE.

04:55.295 --> 04:58.339
I ASKED HIM TO LEAVE,
BUT HE REFUSED.

04:58.339 --> 05:00.260
WHICH IS WHEN YOU CALLED
OFFICER PORTER,

05:00.260 --> 05:01.472
ASKED HIM TO COME OVER?

05:01.472 --> 05:03.263
I WAS SCARED.

05:03.263 --> 05:05.686
BUT I DIDN'T MAKE IT HERE
IN TIME.

05:09.139 --> 05:11.141
FIRST RESPONDERS ARE GONNA BE
HERE IN LESS THAN EIGHT MINUTES.

05:11.141 --> 05:12.272
Emily:
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

05:12.272 --> 05:13.604
[ GRUNTS ]

05:13.604 --> 05:15.195
FOR THE STORY WE'RE GONNA TELL,
THIS NEEDS TO LOOK RIGHT.

05:19.149 --> 05:21.281
WE GOT TO MOVE THIS GLASS.

05:21.281 --> 05:27.157
DANIEL SMASHED THAT PLANTER
THROUGH THE WINDOW.

05:27.157 --> 05:27.998
AND YOU TRIED TO ESCAPE?

05:27.998 --> 05:31.041
UPSTAIRS.

05:31.041 --> 05:34.455
BUT HE FOLLOWED ME.
WE STRUGGLED.

05:34.455 --> 05:39.259
AND HE PUSHED ME.
I-I-I FELL OFF THE BALCONY.

05:39.259 --> 05:40.921
WHEN I SAW HIM COMING
DOWN THE STAIRS,

05:40.921 --> 05:42.092
I KNEW IT WASN'T OVER.

05:42.092 --> 05:43.594
THAT'S WHEN YOU WENT
FOR THE GUN?

05:54.144 --> 05:56.146
TELL ME AGAIN
WHERE YOU GOT IT.

05:59.239 --> 06:01.532
IT MUST HAVE BELONGED
TO A PREVIOUS OWNER.

06:01.532 --> 06:04.825
I-I FOUND IT WHEN I WAS,
UH -- WAS MOVING SOME STUFF

06:04.825 --> 06:05.906
INTO THE ATTIC.

06:05.906 --> 06:08.158
OH, YOU MEAN
THE BASEMENT.

06:10.370 --> 06:11.912
EARLIER, YOU SAID
YOU FOUND THE GUN

06:11.912 --> 06:13.624
WHEN YOU MOVED STUFF
INTO THE BASEMENT.

06:16.206 --> 06:18.589
RIGHT. I'M --
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:18.589 --> 06:19.590
I'M SORRY.

06:19.590 --> 06:21.672
I -- IT'S --
IT'S HARD TO TALK.

06:21.672 --> 06:25.426
UM...I MEANT I WAS MOVING STUFF
FROM THE BASEMENT

06:25.426 --> 06:28.178
INTO THE ATTIC
WHEN I FOUND IT.

06:28.178 --> 06:29.770
IT WAS UNDER A FLOORBOARD.

06:29.770 --> 06:31.101
RIGHT.

06:31.101 --> 06:33.393
YOU'RE NOT GONNA FIND
FLOORBOARDS IN A BASEMENT,

06:33.393 --> 06:35.145
ARE YOU, OFFICER PORTER?

06:35.145 --> 06:37.107
NO, YOU'RE SURE NOT.

06:37.107 --> 06:40.150
SO, ATTIC IT IS.

06:43.193 --> 06:44.525
[ SIGHS ]

06:46.156 --> 06:48.949
David: I'M SORRY.
SHE'S RESTING RIGHT NOW.

06:48.949 --> 06:50.951
IF IT'S ALL THE SAME WITH YOU,
I'D RATHER WAIT.

06:50.951 --> 06:52.202
IF IT'S ALL THE SAME
WITH YOU,

06:52.202 --> 06:54.204
VICTORIA'S IN NO CONDITION
TO TALK TO ANYONE RIGHT NOW.

06:54.204 --> 06:55.205
SHE JUST FOUND OUT.

06:55.205 --> 06:56.376
OH, I APPRECIATE THAT,

06:56.376 --> 06:59.039
BUT THERE ARE QUESTIONS
ABOUT THE CIRCUMSTANCES

06:59.039 --> 07:00.210
OF MR. GRAYSON'S DEATH.

07:00.210 --> 07:02.633
HE WAS SEEN WITH HER
TONIGHT IN MANHATTAN.

07:02.633 --> 07:04.004
HE LEFT ABRUPTLY, AND WE --

07:04.004 --> 07:05.806
YOU WANT TO ASK HER ABOUT
HIS STATE OF MIND,

07:05.806 --> 07:07.097
WHY HE MIGHT ATTACK
HIS EX-WIFE?

07:07.097 --> 07:09.389
DO YOU REALLY THINK
THIS IS A GOOD TIME

07:09.389 --> 07:12.222
TO HAVE THAT CONVERSATION
WITH A GRIEVING MOTHER?

07:12.222 --> 07:14.935
[ SIGHS ]

07:14.935 --> 07:17.978
YOU'RE RIGHT. THIS CAN WAIT.
I'M SORRY TO INTRUDE.

07:19.940 --> 07:22.983
OH, IS THAT YOUR VAN
PARKED OUTSIDE?

07:22.983 --> 07:24.655
YEAH. THIS IS
MY HOUSE. WHY?

07:24.655 --> 07:26.276
YOU LEFT THE KEYS
IN THE REAR DOOR.

07:30.661 --> 07:34.124
OH. WELL,
SAFE NEIGHBORHOOD.

07:34.124 --> 07:36.997
DOESN'T SEEM LIKE IT
LATELY.

07:40.210 --> 07:42.843
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

07:46.847 --> 07:48.088
HOW SMOOTHLY YOU LIE.

07:48.088 --> 07:50.010
I DID THAT SO THAT
YOU DIDN'T HAVE TO.

07:52.052 --> 07:53.644
I WOULDN'T HAVE.

07:53.644 --> 07:56.396
VICTORIA...

07:56.396 --> 07:58.148
I CAN'T IMAGINE
HOW PAINFUL THIS IS.

07:58.148 --> 07:59.229
NO, YOU CAN'T.

08:00.440 --> 08:04.064
TELL ME WHY.

08:04.064 --> 08:05.405
WHAT CRIMES DID DANIEL COMMIT

08:05.405 --> 08:07.277
THAT HE NOT ONLY
PAID WITH HIS LIFE

08:07.277 --> 08:09.109
BUT THAT YOU
EXPECT ME TO TELL

08:09.109 --> 08:11.071
THE MOST VILE,
DESPICABLE LIES ABOUT HIM?

08:11.071 --> 08:12.703
YOU DON'T HAVE TO SAY
ANYTHING TO ANYONE.

08:12.703 --> 08:14.164
ALL RIGHT?
THE STORY WILL BE TOLD --

08:14.164 --> 08:18.208
THE TRUTH IS THAT MY SON GAVE
HIS LIFE FOR YOUR DAUGHTER'S.

08:18.208 --> 08:19.920
NOW HE'S GONE.

08:21.582 --> 08:23.123
[ Voice breaking ] AND
I WILL DIE BEFORE I DESECRATE

08:23.123 --> 08:25.215
HIS NAME LIKE THAT.

08:25.215 --> 08:26.677
WHAT KIND OF MONSTER
WOULD MAKE ME?

08:26.677 --> 08:29.129
IF WE DON'T PULL THIS OFF,
MALCOLM BLACK IS COMING HERE.

08:29.129 --> 08:30.340
HE WILL MAKE YOU,
CHARLOTTE,

08:30.340 --> 08:32.011
AND EVERYONE ELSE
YOU AND I CARE ABOUT

08:32.011 --> 08:33.472
SUFFER MORE THAN YOU KNOW.

08:33.472 --> 08:37.898
YOU KNOW SO MUCH ABOUT HIM,
AND YET HERE WE ARE.

08:37.898 --> 08:39.399
GO TO HELL...

08:39.399 --> 08:42.352
SINCE WE'RE CHOOSING
TO SEND MY SON THERE.

08:51.572 --> 08:52.743
[ SIGHS ]

08:52.743 --> 08:55.115
ALL YOU HAD WAS
OVER-THE-COUNTER STUFF,

08:55.115 --> 08:58.538
BUT THE EMTs CAN GET YOU
SOMETHING STRONGER IF YOU ASK.

08:58.538 --> 09:00.661
NO, I DON'T NEED ANYTHING.

09:00.661 --> 09:04.755
RIGHT. WHY WOULD YOU?
MAYBE YOU CAN ASK FOR ME.

09:08.548 --> 09:10.881
[ SIGHS ]

09:12.222 --> 09:15.135
DANIEL.

09:15.135 --> 09:17.057
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

09:20.270 --> 09:21.892
ARE YOU GONNA BE
ALL RIGHT, JACK?

09:21.892 --> 09:24.184
I'M NOT THE ONE WHO WENT
OVER THE RAILING

09:24.184 --> 09:27.147
AND DISLOCATED MY SHOULDER
AND GOD KNOWS WHAT ELSE.

09:27.147 --> 09:29.740
NO, I MEANT...

09:29.740 --> 09:31.742
KATE.

09:31.742 --> 09:34.114
I KNOW. I KNOW.

09:34.114 --> 09:35.906
I'M JUST NOT LETTING MYSELF
THINK ABOUT IT

09:35.906 --> 09:37.457
TILL WE'RE THROUGH
THE WOODS ON THIS,

09:37.457 --> 09:39.329
AND YOU SHOULD...

09:39.329 --> 09:40.621
PROBABLY DO THE SAME.

09:40.621 --> 09:42.873
MEANING WHAT?

09:42.873 --> 09:46.046
MEANING YOU WERE STRUGGLING
OUT THERE WITH THAT DETECTIVE.

09:46.046 --> 09:47.587
WHAT?

09:47.587 --> 09:50.170
I'M ANSWERING THE QUESTIONS.
I'M -- I'M SELLING THE STORY.

09:50.170 --> 09:51.381
I'M NOT SO SURE.

09:51.381 --> 09:54.174
I'M WATCHING HER REACT TO YOU,
AND I'M TELLING YOU,

09:54.174 --> 09:56.306
IF THEY GET A HINT THAT WE'RE
NOT BEING TRUTHFUL, IT'S --

09:57.638 --> 09:58.769
LOOK, THE POINT IS,

09:58.769 --> 10:00.851
CONSIDERING WHAT
YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH,

10:00.851 --> 10:03.143
IT'S OKAY TO TELL THEM
THAT YOU NEED A BREAK.

10:03.143 --> 10:04.434
EXCEPT THAT I DON'T.

10:04.434 --> 10:05.435
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:05.435 --> 10:06.647
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

10:09.940 --> 10:11.231
HEY.

10:12.993 --> 10:14.154
I JUST WANTED TO LET YOU KNOW

10:14.154 --> 10:15.786
THE DETECTIVES
ARE DONE WITH YOU FOR NOW.

10:15.786 --> 10:17.998
WELL,
THEY DON'T HAVE TO BE.

10:17.998 --> 10:19.619
I MEAN, I CAN KEEP GOING
IF IT WILL HELP.

10:19.619 --> 10:21.161
NO. DETECTIVE ADAMS
SAYS ANY MORE TONIGHT

10:21.161 --> 10:22.542
WILL BE DIMINISHING RETURNS.

10:22.542 --> 10:24.665
SO AS LONG AS YOU MAKE
YOURSELF AVAILABLE TOMORROW,

10:24.665 --> 10:25.505
IF NEED BE --

10:25.505 --> 10:26.416
SO, THEY'RE NOT
BOOKING HER?

10:26.416 --> 10:28.208
NO. NOT TONIGHT.

10:28.208 --> 10:30.590
I'M TRULY SORRY, EMILY.

10:30.590 --> 10:32.302
THANK YOU.

10:39.810 --> 10:41.431
THAT'S A TOUGH CARD
TO DRAW --

10:41.431 --> 10:43.393
HAVING TO SHOOT
YOUR EX POINT-BLANK.

10:43.393 --> 10:45.645
SO, YOU SAW
THE WHOLE THING?

10:45.645 --> 10:46.857
YEAH.

10:46.857 --> 10:50.150
I GOT HERE JUST AS --

10:50.150 --> 10:51.942
JUST RIGHT AT THE END.

10:51.942 --> 10:53.153
I WISH THAT
I HAD BEEN QUICKER.

10:53.153 --> 10:54.234
MAYBE I COULD HAVE
DONE SOMETHING.

10:54.234 --> 10:56.576
YEAH, WELL, IT SOUNDS LIKE
EMILY DIDN'T HAVE MUCH CHOICE,

10:56.576 --> 10:57.948
IF WHAT SHE'S SAYING IS TRUE.

10:59.700 --> 11:01.832
IF WHAT SHE'S SAYING
IS TRUE?

11:01.832 --> 11:03.163
COME ON.
BETWEEN YOU AND ME,

11:03.163 --> 11:05.455
SHE WAS A LITTLE SHAKY
WITH HER FACTS IN THERE.

11:05.455 --> 11:07.748
YOU TRY GETTING THE CRAP
KICKED OUT OF YOU AND
HAVING TO OFF YOUR EX.

11:07.748 --> 11:10.290
WE'LL SEE HOW SHAKY YOU ARE.

11:10.290 --> 11:12.212
NO, YOU'RE RIGHT.

11:12.212 --> 11:17.137
IT'S JUST -- I'VE SEEN EMILY
PLAY PEOPLE, INCLUDING ME.

11:17.137 --> 11:20.180
SHE'S GOOD AT IT.

11:20.180 --> 11:21.972
ANYWAY...

11:21.972 --> 11:24.104
I HOPE IT'S ALL TRUE.

11:24.104 --> 11:25.395
I'LL SEE YOU IN THE MORNING.

11:40.530 --> 11:42.662
NOLAN:
Is she still sleeping?

11:42.662 --> 11:43.663
YEAH, SHE NEEDS IT.

11:43.663 --> 11:45.205
I DON'T THINK
SHE'S UP TO ANOTHER

11:45.205 --> 11:46.166
POLICE INTERROGATION TODAY.

11:46.166 --> 11:48.128
Well, I don't know
if it's abject fear,

11:48.128 --> 11:49.669
BUT I'VE BEEN
CRAZY PRODUCTIVE.

11:49.669 --> 11:52.132
I REVERSE TIME-STAMPED
A CALL FROM EMILY'S PHONE

11:52.132 --> 11:54.464
TO YOURS LAST NIGHT
TO SUPPORT HER STORY.
 Good.

11:54.464 --> 11:56.256
'CAUSE I KNOW ONE COP WHO'S
GONNA BE LOOKING INTO IT.

11:56.256 --> 11:59.259
WELL, ANYONE SEARCHING
FOR AGENT TAYLOR

11:59.259 --> 12:01.051
WILL BEGIN IN MIAMI.

12:01.051 --> 12:03.553
I SENT OUR, UH,
DREAD PIRATE MALCOLM

12:03.553 --> 12:05.105
TEXTS FROM HER PHONE

12:05.105 --> 12:08.058
AND DROPPED A TRAIL
OF DIGITAL BREADCRUMBS

12:08.058 --> 12:11.942
INDICATING A LONG-AWAITED
LAST-MINUTE VACATION.

12:11.942 --> 12:13.193
THAT PHONE'S GONNA
BE A PROBLEM, MAN.

12:13.193 --> 12:14.484
It -- It's got GPS.

12:14.484 --> 12:16.026
IF MALCOLM TRACKS IT,
WE'RE ALL --

12:16.026 --> 12:17.567
DUDE, WHO ARE
YOU TALKING TO?

12:17.567 --> 12:19.659
THE PHONE ARRIVED
IN THE SUNSHINE STATE

12:19.659 --> 12:21.491
BY PRIVATE COURIER
LATE LAST NIGHT

12:21.491 --> 12:23.623
after I'd excavated it,
cloned it,

12:23.623 --> 12:25.786
AND MINED EVERY PIECE
OF DATA FROM IT I COULD.

12:25.786 --> 12:28.288
[ CHUCKLES ]
ANYTHING GOOD?

12:28.288 --> 12:31.131
MM, WELL, I DON'T KNOW.

12:31.131 --> 12:33.373
HOW ABOUT
THE FAA LOCATOR NUMBERS

12:33.373 --> 12:37.217
FOR EVERY ONE OF MALCOLM BLACK'S
PRIVATE PLANES?

12:37.217 --> 12:39.970
ONE OF THEM JUST POPPED UP
ON THE FAA MAP.

12:39.970 --> 12:43.343
IT'S BEING PREPPED
OUTSIDE AN AIRFIELD IN OTTAWA.

12:43.343 --> 12:45.185
THERE'S NO FLIGHT PLAN.

12:45.185 --> 12:47.187
IT COULD BE HEADED TO MIAMI.

12:47.187 --> 12:48.768
OR IT COULD BE COMING HERE.

12:48.768 --> 12:50.190
JACK,
BE A "GLASS HALF FULL" GUY.

12:50.190 --> 12:52.062
WE STILL HAVE TO CLEAN OUT
THE HOTEL ROOM.

12:52.062 --> 12:54.104
I'll meet you there in 10.
 OKAY.

12:56.566 --> 12:58.158
LOUISE.

12:58.158 --> 13:01.281
[ Crying ] DID YOU HEAR
ABOUT DANIEL GRAYSON?

13:01.281 --> 13:03.703
I DID. I'M --
I'M SORRY.

13:03.703 --> 13:06.616
I KNOW YOU TWO
WERE...COLLEAGUES?

13:06.616 --> 13:08.668
OH!

13:08.668 --> 13:13.043
I SUDDENLY FELT SO ALONE, AND
I DIDN'T KNOW WHERE ELSE TO GO.

13:13.043 --> 13:14.174
Shh. Shh. Shh. Shh. Shh.

13:14.174 --> 13:18.008
LOOK, I-I-I KNOW
IT'S A LOT TO ASK,

13:18.008 --> 13:22.382
BUT, UM, COULD I MAYBE STAY HERE
UNTIL I GET MY BEARINGS?

13:22.382 --> 13:25.135
OF COURSE YOU CAN,
AS LONG AS YOU NEED.

13:25.135 --> 13:26.186
MY CASA IS YOUR CASA.

13:26.186 --> 13:27.597
I-I HAVE TO RUN OUT
FOR A MINUTE, BUT I'LL --

13:27.597 --> 13:29.479
WAS IT REALLY
YOUR FRIEND EMILY?

13:29.479 --> 13:32.392
I-I-I DON'T KNOW.
THEY'RE STILL INVESTIGATING.

13:32.392 --> 13:35.025
OH, POOR VICTORIA.
SHE MUST BE A WRECK.

13:35.025 --> 13:37.027
UNDOUBTEDLY.
WE'LL TALK SOON?

13:37.027 --> 13:39.199
YEAH, I THINK I'LL BAKE
SOMETHING FOR HER

13:39.199 --> 13:41.111
BEFORE MY XANAX WEARS OFF.

13:41.111 --> 13:42.442
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

13:42.442 --> 13:44.154
CAN I USE YOUR KITCHEN?

13:44.154 --> 13:46.246
OH.

13:46.246 --> 13:47.657
THANK YOU.

13:50.080 --> 13:52.122
I NEED TO GO OUT.

13:52.122 --> 13:53.413
THE BODY'S STILL IN THE VAN,
AND I NEED TO --

13:53.413 --> 13:54.794
WHO WAS THAT ON THE PHONE?

13:54.794 --> 13:56.126
CHARLOTTE'S DOCTOR.

13:56.126 --> 13:59.719
HE'S GONNA MAKE SURE
THAT SHE DOESN'T COME HOME.

13:59.719 --> 14:01.511
I MEAN, HE THINKS
IT'LL DAMAGE HER RECOVERY.

14:01.511 --> 14:03.673
BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT
YOU TOLD HIM TO THINK.

14:04.554 --> 14:06.386
I'M JUST LOOKING OUT
FOR HER.

14:06.386 --> 14:07.637
HER BROTHER IS DEAD.

14:07.637 --> 14:10.140
WHAT DO YOU THINK
IT'S GOING TO DO TO HER

14:10.140 --> 14:12.312
WHEN SHE HEARS
ALL THESE LIES ABOUT HIM?

14:12.312 --> 14:13.853
WE DON'T HAVE
A CHOICE RIGHT NOW.

14:13.853 --> 14:16.186
I DO. I'M GETTING
OUT OF HERE.

14:16.186 --> 14:17.277
I CAN'T LOOK AT YOU
FOR ANOTHER SECOND,

14:17.277 --> 14:19.069
AND IF I STAY IN THIS HOUSE,
I AM GOING TO LOSE MY MIND.

14:19.069 --> 14:20.400
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
 ANYWHERE BUT HERE!

14:20.400 --> 14:21.942
WHAT DO YOU THINK
IS GONNA HAPPEN

14:21.942 --> 14:23.443
WHEN THE FIRST PERSON
ASKS YOU ABOUT DANIEL?

14:23.443 --> 14:25.485
THE STORM COMES IN.

14:25.485 --> 14:27.037
NONE OF US SURVIVE
TILL SUNSET.

14:27.037 --> 14:29.119
I WON'T BE A PRISONER
TO YOUR LIES ANYMORE.

14:29.119 --> 14:31.081
I WAS A PRISONER FOR TWO DECADES
BECAUSE OF YOURS.

14:31.081 --> 14:33.083
YOU CAN HOLD ON
ONE MORE DAY.

14:35.045 --> 14:36.126
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:41.001 --> 14:44.174
WERE YOU THIS CRUEL 20 YEARS AGO
AND I JUST MISSED IT?

14:44.174 --> 14:47.807
BACK THEN, YOU BETRAYED ME
TO KEEP DANIEL ALIVE.

14:47.807 --> 14:50.350
ARE YOU REALLY GONNA DO IT AGAIN
NOW TO PROTECT HIS MEMORY?

14:50.350 --> 14:51.681
IT'S YOUR CALL.

14:53.563 --> 14:55.565
I WON'T BE RESPONSIBLE
FOR ANYONE'S DEATH,

14:55.565 --> 15:00.110
BUT I AM GOING
TO MOURN MY SON.

15:00.110 --> 15:01.982
AND I WON'T STAY HERE.

15:09.869 --> 15:11.161
VICTORIA'S GONNA
STAY HERE FOR NOW.

15:11.161 --> 15:13.033
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?
 THIS ISN'T MY DOING.

15:13.033 --> 15:14.834
NO. THIS IS HAPPENING.
 WHAT PART OF "NO"
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND?

15:14.834 --> 15:16.456
THIS IS MY HOUSE,
NOT YOURS OR HERS.

15:16.456 --> 15:18.248
DAVID, LISTEN TO YOUR
DAUGHTER. IN TRYING TO
PREVENT ONE DISASTER,

15:18.248 --> 15:20.500
YOU'RE SOWING THE SEEDS
FOR AN EVEN CRUELER ONE.
 AFTER EVERYTHING
THAT HAPPENED,

15:20.500 --> 15:22.002
IT WILL BE A COLD-ASS DAY IN
HELL IF SHE STAYS ANOTHER --

15:22.002 --> 15:25.255
THERE IS NO CHANCE --
 ENOUGH! THE BOTH OF YOU!

15:25.255 --> 15:27.007
IF WE HAVE ANY HOPE
OF GETTING THROUGH THIS ALIVE,

15:27.007 --> 15:29.179
THIS IS OUR ONLY CHANCE.
YOU WANT TO BE ALONE?

15:29.179 --> 15:30.430
THIS IS A BIG, SAFE HOUSE
TO BE ALONE IN...

15:30.430 --> 15:32.262
WITH SOMEONE WHO CAN WATCH YOU.

15:32.262 --> 15:34.184
WHY DON'T YOU WATCH HER?

15:34.184 --> 15:35.645
BECAUSE I HAVE
A BODY TO MOVE.

15:35.645 --> 15:37.057
I HAVE TO CLEAN UP
YOUR MESS.

15:37.057 --> 15:38.318
MY MESS?!
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?!

15:38.318 --> 15:39.819
WHY IN THE HELL WOULD --

15:39.819 --> 15:41.982
'CAUSE I SAID SO, THAT'S WHY!
I WAS VERY CLEAR WITH YOU.

15:41.982 --> 15:44.154
I SAID STAY OUT OF THIS
MALCOLM BLACK BUSINESS,

15:44.154 --> 15:45.155
BUT YOU DIDN'T.

15:45.155 --> 15:47.027
NOW YOU'RE GONNA LISTEN.

15:47.027 --> 15:49.159
I CAN'T WATCH VICTORIA, AND
I CAN'T HAVE HER BEING ALONE.

15:49.159 --> 15:50.370
THIS HOUSE IS A FORTRESS.

15:50.370 --> 15:51.701
THERE'S PLENTY OF ROOM
FOR THE TWO OF YOU.

15:51.701 --> 15:53.413
SO FOR THE TIME BEING,
YOU'RE BOTH GONNA STAY HERE.

15:53.413 --> 15:56.036
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

15:57.877 --> 15:59.499
GOOD.

15:59.499 --> 16:01.171
PLAY NICE.

16:03.463 --> 16:05.215
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:18.018 --> 16:19.359
I GOT INTO
THE RESERVATION DATABASE

16:19.359 --> 16:21.441
AND CHECKED KATE OUT AS OF
LAST NIGHT, BUT FROZE THE ROOM.

16:21.441 --> 16:23.403
I'M GONNA GO CHECK OUT
THE SECURITY MONITORS.

16:23.403 --> 16:25.065
YOU START PACKING.
CARD KEY FOR HER ROOM.

16:25.065 --> 16:27.277
YEAH, I...
ALREADY HAVE ONE.

16:27.277 --> 16:28.908
YEAH, YOURS IS GONNA LEAVE
A RECORD OF ACCESS.

16:28.908 --> 16:29.699
THIS ONE'S CLEAN.

16:29.699 --> 16:32.202
GO.

16:34.534 --> 16:35.955
Victoria: MARGAUX.

16:35.955 --> 16:37.997
I WENT TO THE BEACH HOUSE.

16:37.997 --> 16:40.920
IT WAS EMPTY.
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

16:40.920 --> 16:43.963
IT WAS DECIDED
I COULDN'T BE ALONE.

16:43.963 --> 16:46.336
AND EMILY?
IS SHE HERE?

16:46.336 --> 16:49.339
SOMEWHERE UPSTAIRS.

16:50.470 --> 16:53.183
I'M SO...

16:53.183 --> 16:55.185
[ SOBBING ]

17:26.756 --> 17:27.877
DROP IT!

17:35.765 --> 17:37.437
Nolan: JACK.

17:37.437 --> 17:39.229
JACK.

17:39.229 --> 17:41.060
ARE YOU OKAY?

17:42.812 --> 17:45.985
LOOK, SHE WAS BAD NEWS.

17:45.985 --> 17:49.068
SHE WAS GOING TO KILL EMILY.

17:49.068 --> 17:53.113
YOU DIDN'T HAVE ANY CHOICE.

17:53.113 --> 17:54.404
[ SIGHS ]

17:54.404 --> 17:56.116
WHEN I TOOK THIS JOB,
IN THE BACK OF MY MIND,

17:56.116 --> 17:58.998
I ALWAYS KNEW THAT THERE
WAS A CHANCE I'D HAVE TO...

18:02.081 --> 18:03.873
SHE JUST WASN'T
THE PERSON THAT I THOUGHT...

18:03.873 --> 18:06.796
I GET IT.

18:06.796 --> 18:09.129
I WILL DOING ANYTHING
I CAN TO HELP.

18:09.129 --> 18:10.089
BUT RIGHT NOW,

18:10.089 --> 18:12.472
WE HAVE 12 MINUTES TILL
THE CLEANING WOMAN COMES.

18:12.472 --> 18:13.973
WE GOT TO GET PACKING NOW.

18:35.074 --> 18:36.786
[ SNIFFS ]

18:40.700 --> 18:43.623
WHAT I HEARD FROM
THE POLICE MAKES NO SENSE.

18:43.623 --> 18:45.875
SHE'S CLAIMING
HE ATTACKED HER?

18:45.875 --> 18:49.169
SHE HAD TO SHOOT HIM?
SELF-DEFENSE?

18:49.169 --> 18:52.382
WHAT HAPPENED...

18:52.382 --> 18:55.175
HAS BEEN HARD FOR ALL OF US
TO ACCEPT.

18:55.175 --> 18:59.309
BUT I DON'T ACCEPT IT,
AND YOU CAN'T, EITHER.

18:59.309 --> 19:01.601
THE POLICE MUST HEAR
THE TRUTH FROM US.

19:01.601 --> 19:04.103
WHEN I LAST SPOKE WITH DANIEL,
HE WAS HAPPY,

19:04.103 --> 19:08.528
COMMITTED TO TURNING HIS LIFE
AROUND, TO SPENDING IT WITH ME,

19:08.528 --> 19:10.069
TO BEING A FAMILY.

19:10.069 --> 19:12.442
HE DID LOVE YOU, MARGAUX.

19:12.442 --> 19:15.114
THAT'S HOW I KNOW
SHE'S LYING.

19:15.114 --> 19:16.616
DANIEL HAD MOVED ON
FROM EMILY.

19:16.616 --> 19:18.448
HE HAD NO REASON
TO COME TO HER HOUSE.

19:18.448 --> 19:21.080
SHE LURED HIM HERE,
THEN KILLED HIM IN COLD BLOOD.

19:21.080 --> 19:22.662
YOU OF ALL PEOPLE
SHOULD KNOW THAT.

19:26.706 --> 19:28.087
BUT I DON'T.

19:29.749 --> 19:31.341
I DON'T KNOW THAT.

19:31.341 --> 19:33.132
HOW CAN YOU SAY THAT?

19:33.132 --> 19:35.004
BECAUSE I KNOW THE TRUTH.

19:35.004 --> 19:39.058
DANIEL AND EMILY COULD
NEVER ESCAPE ONE ANOTHER.

19:39.058 --> 19:41.180
AND WHAT SHE INFLICTED
UPON HIM

19:41.180 --> 19:42.802
WAS SOMETHING
HE COULD NEVER FORGET,

19:42.802 --> 19:46.566
AND I WILL ALWAYS HATE HER
FOR IT.

19:46.566 --> 19:49.188
BUT IT'S WHY
I ALSO BELIEVE HER.

19:51.651 --> 19:55.445
THEN I'LL GO TO
THE POLICE WITHOUT YOU.

19:59.319 --> 20:01.160
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

20:02.242 --> 20:03.783
YOU'RE WELCOME.

20:06.165 --> 20:10.460
[ SPEAKING FRENCH ]

20:10.460 --> 20:14.884
[ SIREN WAILING ]

20:31.901 --> 20:34.904
EMILY.

20:34.904 --> 20:35.985
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

20:35.985 --> 20:37.447
THEY SAID THEY HAD
MORE QUESTIONS.

20:37.447 --> 20:41.030
YOU DIDN'T HAVE TO COME BY.

20:41.030 --> 20:43.072
I TALKED TO BEN AND ADAMS
AND I GOT YOU A DAY TO RECOVER.

20:43.072 --> 20:44.414
I'M FINE.

20:44.414 --> 20:46.075
IT'S YOU INTERVENING THAT
WILL MAKE ME LOOK SUSPICIOUS.

20:46.075 --> 20:47.497
YOU'RE WRONG --
EVERYONE HERE UNDERSTANDS

20:47.497 --> 20:48.918
WHAT YOU WENT THROUGH.

20:48.918 --> 20:50.290
NO ONE'S GONNA THINK TWICE
ABOUT GIVING YOU MORE TIME

20:50.290 --> 20:51.371
UNLESS YOU GIVE THEM
REASON TO.

20:51.371 --> 20:52.372
LOOK, THIS IS NOT
YOUR CALL TO MAKE.

20:52.372 --> 20:53.373
YES, IT IS.

20:53.373 --> 20:55.715
I HAVE EVERY BIT AS MUCH
TO LOSE AS YOU.

20:55.715 --> 20:57.587
I WAS THERE LAST NIGHT,
TOO, AND I SAW WHAT
HAPPENED AFTERWARD.

20:57.587 --> 20:59.138
IT WAS A COUPLE OF ANSWERS.
NO ONE EVEN NOTICED.

20:59.138 --> 21:00.430
BEN NOTICED.

21:00.430 --> 21:01.551
WELL, IF THAT'S TRUE,

21:01.551 --> 21:02.842
ALL THE MORE REASON
TO SHOW UP AND FIX IT.

21:02.842 --> 21:04.183
OR BLOW IT FOR ALL OF US.

21:04.183 --> 21:05.385
[ SIGHS ]

21:05.385 --> 21:07.016
LOOK, MY ALIBI WILL HOLD.

21:07.016 --> 21:08.688
I'VE DONE THIS A MILLION TIMES.
I KNOW WHAT I'M DOING.

21:08.688 --> 21:11.230
YES, YOU'VE DONE THIS A MILLION
TIMES, BUT YOU ARE ONLY HUMAN.

21:11.230 --> 21:13.022
AND YOU ARE STRUGGLING
THIS TIME,

21:13.022 --> 21:15.154
BECAUSE WHAT HAPPENED
LAST NIGHT IS TRAUMATIC

21:15.154 --> 21:16.736
AND IT IS GOING
TO HAVE AN EFFECT.

21:16.736 --> 21:18.898
TAKE THE DAY OFF.
GET YOUR HEAD TOGETHER.

21:18.898 --> 21:20.360
GRIEVE.
IT'S WHAT HUMANS DO.

21:20.360 --> 21:22.241
[ SIGHS ]

21:22.241 --> 21:24.824
LOOK, JACK,
JUST WORRY ABOUT YOURSELF.

21:24.824 --> 21:25.955
MY HEAD IS JUST FINE.

21:30.039 --> 21:33.082
THIS LICENSE
IS STILL TEMPORARY.

21:33.082 --> 21:36.416
YEAH, I HAVEN'T REALLY HAD
A CHANCE TO UPDATE MY PAPERWORK,

21:36.416 --> 21:38.177
BUT I WILL GET ON THAT.

21:38.177 --> 21:39.379
SO, IF WE'RE DONE...

21:39.379 --> 21:42.181
YOU SEEM TO BE IN A HURRY.

21:42.181 --> 21:44.183
DIDN'T EVEN ASK
WHY I STOPPED YOU.

21:45.555 --> 21:47.186
YOUR TAILLIGHT'S OUT.

21:47.186 --> 21:50.480
REALLY?
I DON'T THINK SO.

21:50.480 --> 21:52.812
LET'S TAKE A LOOK.

22:05.905 --> 22:09.449
OH, YEAH.

22:12.502 --> 22:13.953
LOOK AT THAT.

22:13.953 --> 22:16.215
IT'S ALMOST LIKE SOMEONE
INTENTIONALLY SMASHED IT.

22:16.215 --> 22:18.878
OPEN THE BACK
OF THE VAN.

22:18.878 --> 22:20.420
I DON'T THINK SO.

22:20.420 --> 22:21.761
YOU DON'T HAVE CAUSE.

22:21.761 --> 22:24.924
MY CAUSE IF THAT YOU'RE
A SKETCHY SON OF A BITCH.

22:24.924 --> 22:26.846
YOU MAY HAVE FOOLED
A LOT OF PEOPLE,

22:26.846 --> 22:28.928
BUT I KNOW YOU'RE
HIDING SOMETHING.

22:28.928 --> 22:30.059
OPEN IT.

22:30.059 --> 22:31.851
THIS ISN'T ABOUT ME,
IS IT?

22:31.851 --> 22:33.683
IT'S ABOUT
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

22:33.683 --> 22:35.234
I'M JUST THE GUY STANDING
IN BETWEEN YOU

22:35.234 --> 22:37.397
AND A WOMAN WHO WON'T
GIVE YOU THE TIME OF DAY.

22:37.397 --> 22:38.438
AM I RIGHT?

22:38.438 --> 22:41.030
OPEN IT OR I WILL.

23:01.711 --> 23:03.803
GET THAT TAILLIGHT FIXED.

23:14.143 --> 23:16.646
I WAS TAUGHT
TO DEFLECT GRIEF

23:16.646 --> 23:19.609
WITH BAKED GOODS
AND COMFORT FOOD,

23:19.609 --> 23:21.280
THUS THE ABUNDANCE
OF STARCHES.

23:21.280 --> 23:24.113
THANK YOU, LOUISE.
THAT'S VERY THOUGHTFUL.

23:26.656 --> 23:30.329
I KNOW MY RELATIONSHIP
WITH YOUR SON WAS...

23:30.329 --> 23:33.122
BRIEF, BUT IN THAT TIME,

23:33.122 --> 23:37.296
IT WAS CLEAR THAT DANNY
HAD A SPIRIT OF COMPASSION,

23:37.296 --> 23:38.918
DECENCY, AND GOODNESS.

23:39.999 --> 23:42.171
LIKE HIS MOTHER.

23:42.171 --> 23:45.044
I APPRECIATE THAT.

23:45.044 --> 23:47.346
OH.

23:47.346 --> 23:51.050
I AM SO SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

23:53.813 --> 23:55.975
WELL, I'M SURE
YOU'RE EXHAUSTED,

23:55.975 --> 23:59.268
AND I LEFT NOLAN ROSS' KITCHEN
A COMPLETE MESS,

23:59.268 --> 24:00.730
SO I SHOULD GO.

24:00.730 --> 24:03.062
YOU'RE FRIENDS
WITH MR. ROSS?

24:03.062 --> 24:04.614
YES, I-I'M ACTUALLY
STAYING WITH HIM.

24:08.157 --> 24:11.160
LOUISE,
I HATE TO IMPOSE, BU--

24:11.160 --> 24:14.283
BUT DO YOU THINK MAYBE YOU
COULD SIT WITH ME FOR A BIT?

24:16.335 --> 24:17.837
YES.

24:17.837 --> 24:19.959
YES, OF COURSE.
I'M HERE FOR YOU.

24:19.959 --> 24:21.040
ANYTHING YOU NEED.

24:23.212 --> 24:28.047
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

24:28.047 --> 24:29.048
TALK TO ME.

24:29.048 --> 24:31.641
GUESS WHOSE PLANE
JUST TOOK OFF.

24:31.641 --> 24:34.934
NOLAN, DEAR, VICTORIA
APPRECIATED THE PIE SO MUCH

24:34.934 --> 24:37.937
THAT NOW
I'M THINKING CUPCAKES.

24:37.937 --> 24:39.398
DO YOU MIND?

24:39.398 --> 24:40.980
IT'S ALL YOURS.

24:40.980 --> 24:42.692
DAVID:
Where's he headed?

24:42.692 --> 24:44.403
SOUTH.
HE'S HEADED SOUTH.

24:44.403 --> 24:45.274
IT'S ALL SOUTH
FROM CANADA.

24:45.274 --> 24:46.405
IS HE AIMING AT THE HAMPTONS

24:46.405 --> 24:48.738
or chasing his daughter's
phone to Miami?

24:48.738 --> 24:50.990
DAVID, WE'RE NOT GONNA KNOW
FOR A FEW HOURS.

24:50.990 --> 24:53.032
YOU JUST...
HAVE TO HANG TIGHT.

24:53.032 --> 24:55.164
I'm learning
that's not my strength.

24:55.164 --> 24:56.996
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

24:58.878 --> 25:01.380
[ NOLAN WHISPERING ]

25:12.181 --> 25:14.303
DETECTIVE ADAMS
IS STILL OUT IN THE FIELD.

25:14.303 --> 25:16.556
SHE'LL JOIN US AS SOON
AS SHE GETS BACK,

25:16.556 --> 25:18.187
BUT IF YOU'RE SURE
THAT YOU'RE OKAY --

25:18.187 --> 25:19.639
YEAH, I-I'M SURE.

25:19.639 --> 25:22.481
I KNOW THERE WAS A DISCREPANCY
LAST NIGHT WITH THE, UH --

25:22.481 --> 25:24.193
OH, WHERE YOU FIRST
FOUND THE GUN.

25:24.193 --> 25:25.985
YEAH.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

25:25.985 --> 25:27.356
DISCREPANCIES HAPPEN.

25:27.356 --> 25:29.528
IT'S NOT REALLY A CONCERN.

25:29.528 --> 25:32.612
BUT THE MEDICAL EXAMINER'S
REPORT --

25:32.612 --> 25:34.073
I MEAN,
THAT COULD BE A PROBLEM.

25:34.073 --> 25:35.414
SEE, LAST NIGHT,

25:35.414 --> 25:37.076
YOU SAID YOU THOUGHT DANIEL HAD
BEEN DRINKING WHEN HE SHOWED UP.

25:37.076 --> 25:38.537
I DID. YEAH.

25:38.537 --> 25:40.499
BUT THE M.E.'s REPORT SHOWS
NO ALCOHOL IN HIS SYSTEM.

25:40.499 --> 25:42.792
ALL RIGHT, SO,
THAT'S WEIRD.

25:42.792 --> 25:45.214
I MEAN, WE CAN RUN IT AGAIN.
MAYBE HE MISSED IT.

25:45.214 --> 25:48.337
MORE LIKELY I WAS WRONG
AND MISJUDGED HIM.

25:48.337 --> 25:49.929
I MEAN [CHUCKLES]

25:49.929 --> 25:53.092
DANIEL DIDN'T NEED ALCOHOL TO
GET VIOLENT AND ANGRY WITH ME.

25:53.092 --> 25:56.976
I WAS ACTUALLY JUST TALKING TO
DANIEL'S GIRLFRIEND ABOUT THAT.

25:56.976 --> 25:59.098
MARGAUX LeMARCHAL?

25:59.098 --> 26:01.560
SHE SWORE UP AND DOWN
THAT DANIEL WASN'T ANGRY

26:01.560 --> 26:04.143
OR VIOLENT OR ANYTHING.

26:04.143 --> 26:07.066
YOU KNOW, IN FACT,
ACCORDING TO HER,

26:07.066 --> 26:10.189
HE WAS AS HAPPY
AS SHE'D EVER SEEN HIM.

26:10.189 --> 26:13.192
HE WAS EXCITED
THAT HE WAS GONNA BE A FATHER.

26:17.116 --> 26:20.620
I'M SORRY,
DID YOU JUST SAY...

26:20.620 --> 26:22.001
A FATHER?

26:22.001 --> 26:24.664
YEAH, YOU DIDN'T...KNOW?

26:28.838 --> 26:30.339
I'M SORRY.
I THINK I'M GONNA NEED A BREAK.

26:30.339 --> 26:31.801
OH, OF COURSE.

26:31.801 --> 26:33.552
UH, WOULD YOU MIND IF I ASKED
YOU JUST ONE MORE QUESTION?

26:33.552 --> 26:35.054
WHAT?

26:35.054 --> 26:37.637
DANIEL ATTACKED YOU,
RIGHT?

26:37.637 --> 26:39.268
BUT HE HAD NO BRUISES,
NO CUTS.

26:39.268 --> 26:41.931
I MEAN, HE HAD -- HE HAD NO
DEFENSIVE WOUNDS OF ANY SORT.

26:43.222 --> 26:45.815
TELL ME WHY I SHOULDN'T
FIND THAT CURIOUS...

26:45.815 --> 26:48.648
ESPECIALLY SINCE
YOU'VE ALWAYS STRUCK ME

26:48.648 --> 26:51.230
AS SOMEONE WHO COULD
HOLD HER OWN IN A FIGHT.

26:54.153 --> 26:56.826
HE'S BAITING YOU, EMILY.
GET OUT OF THERE.

26:56.826 --> 27:02.121
DANIEL WAS UNHURT BECAUSE...

27:02.121 --> 27:05.004
I DIDN'T WANT TO HURT DANIEL.

27:05.004 --> 27:08.337
EVEN WHEN HE ATTACKED ME,
I HELD BACK.

27:08.337 --> 27:09.248
WHY?

27:09.248 --> 27:13.132
BECAUSE WHAT HE WAS SAYING
WAS TRUE.

27:13.132 --> 27:16.095
I HAD HURT HIM.

27:16.095 --> 27:21.470
I MARRIED HIM FOR
THE WRONG REASONS, AND WHEN...

27:21.470 --> 27:23.763
WHEN IT ALL FELL APART,

27:23.763 --> 27:28.027
IT WAS LIKE I THREW
A GRENADE INTO HIS LIFE.

27:28.027 --> 27:32.321
THE DAMAGE THAT
I CAUSED WAS REAL,

27:32.321 --> 27:34.904
AND I KNEW IT AT THE TIME.

27:34.904 --> 27:38.037
I WOULDN'T HURT HIM
BECAUSE...

27:38.037 --> 27:43.202
UNDERNEATH ALL
OF THE SCAR TISSUE AND...

27:44.874 --> 27:47.787
THE FLAWS, THE TEMPER...

27:52.001 --> 27:54.423
...THERE WAS
A GENUINELY GOOD GUY

27:54.423 --> 27:58.888
JUST TRYING
TO FIND HIS WAY.

27:58.888 --> 28:01.100
SO, DESPITE OUR HISTORY,

28:01.100 --> 28:05.264
DESPITE EVERYTHING
THAT I TOLD MYSELF...

28:09.018 --> 28:10.980
...I CARED ABOUT HIM.

28:13.362 --> 28:16.485
BUT YOU STILL SHOT HIM.

28:16.485 --> 28:20.409
ONLY WHEN I KNEW
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE.

28:22.701 --> 28:25.995
ONLY WHEN I KNEW
HE INTENDED TO KILL ME.

28:25.995 --> 28:29.038
WHY WOULD YOU THINK THAT?

28:29.038 --> 28:33.332
BECAUSE HE TRIED IT BEFORE...

28:33.332 --> 28:34.794
THE NIGHT OF OUR WEDDING.

28:34.794 --> 28:37.006
ON THE BOAT.

28:37.006 --> 28:39.218
I'D HEARD ABOUT THAT, BUT
I-I ALWAYS THOUGHT THAT HE --

28:39.218 --> 28:40.009
I COVERED FOR HIM.

28:41.220 --> 28:45.104
IT WAS THE NIGHT THAT HE LEARNED
I WASN'T IN LOVE WITH HIM.

28:48.397 --> 28:51.150
IT ALMOST DESTROYED
DANIEL, SO...

28:54.023 --> 28:56.025
...HE ALMOST DESTROYED ME.

28:57.907 --> 29:01.160
DANIEL SAID THAT WAS THE NIGHT
THAT I RUINED HIS LIFE.

29:06.916 --> 29:10.039
TURNS OUT HE WAS WRONG.
[ SNIFFLES ]

29:10.039 --> 29:12.291
[ SIGHS ]

29:26.385 --> 29:28.187
Nolan: HIS AIRPLANE JUST
ENTERED NEW YORK AIRSPACE,

29:28.187 --> 29:30.559
SO HE'S EITHER GONNA
HANG A LOUIE AT LONG ISLAND

29:30.559 --> 29:32.231
OR HE'S GONNA KEEP
HEADING SOUTH.

29:32.231 --> 29:34.193
ANY MINUTE NOW.

29:34.193 --> 29:36.025
HOW'S SHE DOING?

29:36.025 --> 29:37.987
ASK HER.

29:37.987 --> 29:39.198
I'M ASKING YOU.

29:39.198 --> 29:43.072
HOW DO YOU THINK SHE'S DOING?
SHE LOST HER SON.

29:43.072 --> 29:47.206
[ SIGHS ]

29:47.206 --> 29:48.828
I AM SORRY ABOUT DANIEL.

29:50.369 --> 29:51.831
I KNOW.

29:53.172 --> 29:55.174
THAT'S IT, FOLKS.

29:55.174 --> 29:57.006
HIS PLANE JUST PASSED OVER
NEW YORK.

29:57.006 --> 29:58.878
SOMEONE IS HEADED
FOR DISNEY WORLD.

29:58.878 --> 29:59.919
THAT'S A RELIEF.

29:59.919 --> 30:01.510
OKAY, SO WE BOUGHT
OURSELVES SOME TIME.

30:01.510 --> 30:02.681
BUT WHAT NOW?

30:02.681 --> 30:04.303
WHEN MALCOLM DOESN'T FIND
WHAT HE'S LOOKING FOR,

30:04.303 --> 30:06.055
I CAN GUARANTEE MIAMI'S
NOT GONNA BE HIS LAST STOP.

30:06.055 --> 30:09.098
YOU SEE, I'M HOPING
THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT IT IS.

30:09.098 --> 30:10.980
WHAT DID YOU DO?

30:10.980 --> 30:13.392
WELL, YOU DON'T GET
TO BE MALCOLM BLACK

30:13.392 --> 30:16.025
WITHOUT HAVING SOME ENEMIES --
COMPETITIVE DEALERS,

30:16.025 --> 30:19.859
CARTEL LEADERS --
ALL EQUALLY BLOOD-THIRSTY.

30:19.859 --> 30:22.071
Nolan: MM. MADE SOME CALLS,
DID YOU?

30:22.071 --> 30:23.782
I SUGGESTED
THEY VISIT MIAMI --

30:23.782 --> 30:25.284
WHERE, WHEN,
THE WHOLE ITINERARY.

30:25.284 --> 30:26.655
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:26.655 --> 30:28.998
OH, YOU ARE ONE BAD-ASS
TRAVEL AGENT, MR. CLARKE.

30:28.998 --> 30:30.209
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

30:30.209 --> 30:32.912
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

30:40.629 --> 30:41.630
[ SIGHS ]

30:48.928 --> 30:51.230
MARGAUX.

30:51.230 --> 30:53.182
I'M SO SORRY
ABOUT DANIEL.

30:53.182 --> 30:56.475
I CAN'T IMAGINE WHAT
YOU'RE GOING THROUGH.

30:56.475 --> 30:58.067
PLEASE, COME. SIT.

30:58.067 --> 30:59.438
NO.

30:59.438 --> 31:01.941
I WON'T BE HERE
THAT LONG.

31:01.941 --> 31:04.984
MY ATTORNEY JUST SPOKE
WITH THE POLICE.

31:04.984 --> 31:06.245
APPARENTLY,

31:06.245 --> 31:10.489
THEY WILL NOT BE NAMING YOU
AS A SUSPECT IN DANIEL'S MURDER.

31:10.489 --> 31:13.662
DID YOU KNOW?
SELF-DEFENSE.

31:13.662 --> 31:16.455
THEY'RE GOING
TO MAKE THAT OFFICIAL.

31:16.455 --> 31:17.296
MARGAUX --

31:17.296 --> 31:19.298
NO. YOU NEED TO LISTEN.

31:19.298 --> 31:21.090
I KNOW YOU'RE LYING.

31:21.090 --> 31:25.094
YOU PLAYED A GAME WITH
THE POLICE, WITH VICTORIA,

31:25.094 --> 31:27.096
WITH WHO KNOWS
HOW MANY OTHERS,

31:27.096 --> 31:30.309
BUT BELIEVE ME
WHEN I TELL YOU,

31:30.309 --> 31:33.272
I...DO NOT PLAY.

31:34.563 --> 31:35.935
I KNOW YOU MURDERED
DANIEL.

31:35.935 --> 31:38.687
I DID NOT. AND I AM
JUST AS DEVASTATED --

31:38.687 --> 31:42.071
STOP TALKING
AND HEAR ME!

31:42.071 --> 31:44.733
I'M GOING TO MAKE IT
MY LIFE'S JOURNEY

31:44.733 --> 31:46.155
TO SEE YOU PAY
FOR WHAT YOU'VE DONE,

31:46.155 --> 31:49.868
AND THAT JOURNEY
BEGINS NOW!

31:49.868 --> 31:53.582
WE BURY DANIEL ON FRIDAY.

31:53.582 --> 31:55.534
YOU WILL NOT BE THERE.

31:55.534 --> 31:57.746
YOU CAN'T DO THAT,
MARGAUX.

31:57.746 --> 32:00.129
NO. BUT SHE CAN.

32:06.175 --> 32:07.756
I SEE.

32:22.441 --> 32:23.983
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

32:23.983 --> 32:26.325
THANK YOU
FOR YOUR HOSPITALITY.

32:27.987 --> 32:29.568
I'LL BE GOING HOME NOW.

32:33.202 --> 32:37.456
YOU KNOW THAT DANIEL WOULD
HAVE WANTED ME AT HIS FUNERAL.

32:41.130 --> 32:44.293
MAYBE.

32:44.293 --> 32:46.885
BUT WE'LL NEVER KNOW,
WILL WE?

32:51.390 --> 32:52.391
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

33:07.366 --> 33:09.068
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

33:09.068 --> 33:12.201
YES. IT'S PERFECT.

33:12.201 --> 33:13.532
BUT -- BUT THE, UH --

33:13.532 --> 33:15.374
THE TIE?
IT'S THE TIE, RIGHT?

33:15.374 --> 33:17.076
NO, THE --
THE TIE IS FINE.

33:17.076 --> 33:19.038
BUT THE KNOT --
IT'S A LITTLE --

33:19.038 --> 33:20.499
IT'S A LITTLE LUMPY,
RIGHT?

33:20.499 --> 33:21.380
MM-HMM.

33:21.380 --> 33:22.961
I DON'T KNOW.
I TRIED THREE TIMES.

33:22.961 --> 33:23.962
LET ME.

33:23.962 --> 33:25.044
UGH, TELL ME THIS --

33:25.044 --> 33:27.506
WHAT KIND OF GROWN MAN
STILL NEEDS HELP WITH A TIE?

33:27.506 --> 33:30.469
A MAN WHO I THINK CAN DO IT
WITH HIS EYES CLOSED

33:30.469 --> 33:32.841
BUT STILL WANTS HIS MOTHER
TO FEEL WORTHWHILE.

33:32.841 --> 33:34.633
[ CHUCKLES ]
 PAY ATTENTION.

33:34.633 --> 33:37.396
SOON YOU'RE GOING TO BE TEACHING
YOUR OWN SON HOW TO DO IT.

33:38.897 --> 33:39.898
DONE.

33:39.898 --> 33:41.019
HMM?

33:41.019 --> 33:42.401
LET'S SEE.

34:07.296 --> 34:10.089
David: AMANDA.

34:10.089 --> 34:13.222
WE'RE JUST ON THE WAY
TO THE CEMETERY.

34:13.222 --> 34:15.674
I THOUGHT I'D
CHECK IN ON YOU.

34:15.674 --> 34:16.594
YOU OKAY?

34:16.594 --> 34:19.098
SURE.

34:19.098 --> 34:21.270
WHERE'S YOUR LADY FRIEND?

34:21.270 --> 34:23.732
SHE'S WAITING IN THE LIMO.

34:25.853 --> 34:28.687
JUST TELL ME THIS.

34:28.687 --> 34:31.989
A FEW NIGHTS AGO,
BEFORE THE WHEELS CAME OFF,

34:31.989 --> 34:35.114
YOU SAID THAT THIS WOULD
ALL BE OVER SOON,

34:35.114 --> 34:36.034
THAT IT WAS ALL PART
OF A LARGER PLAN.

34:36.034 --> 34:37.116
WHAT DID YOU MEAN?

34:37.116 --> 34:39.578
I CAN'T -- I'M NOT
DOING THIS RIGHT NOW.

34:39.578 --> 34:41.580
PLEASE. I NEED TO KNOW.

34:41.580 --> 34:43.752
WHAT WAS THE PLAN?

34:43.752 --> 34:47.835
IF ALL THIS
HADN'T HAPPENED,

34:47.835 --> 34:51.670
WE'D BE HAVING HER FUNERAL
RIGHT NOW INSTEAD OF DANIEL'S.

34:56.054 --> 34:58.557
YOU WERE GONNA KILL
VICTORIA?

35:03.932 --> 35:04.983
AND NOW?

35:07.146 --> 35:09.278
[ SIGHS ]
I'M GONNA BE LATE.

35:16.034 --> 35:18.076
ADAMS TOLD ME THAT YOU
WERE A REAL ASSET

35:18.076 --> 35:20.038
ON THE, UH,
DANIEL GRAYSON SHOOTING

35:20.038 --> 35:22.831
AND I'M A FOOL IF I DON'T THINK
ABOUT MAKING YOU A DETECTIVE.

35:22.831 --> 35:24.953
WELL, I'D NEVER CALL YOU
A FOOL, SIR.

35:24.953 --> 35:26.955
YEAH. FIND ME TOMORROW.
WE'LL CHAT.

35:26.955 --> 35:28.207
WELL, I CAN CHAT NOW.

35:28.207 --> 35:29.047
I CAN'T DO IT.

35:29.047 --> 35:30.379
THANKS TO YOUR PARTNER,

35:30.379 --> 35:33.051
I GOT, UH, PAPERWORK THAT'S
GONNA KEEP ME HERE PAST DINNER.

35:33.051 --> 35:33.842
MY PARTNER?

35:33.842 --> 35:35.884
LAST-MINUTE FURLOUGH CHANGES,

35:35.884 --> 35:38.217
HE WANTS PERSONAL DAYS --

35:38.217 --> 35:39.137
YOU GUYS DON'T TALK?

35:44.893 --> 35:48.106
HEY. WHAT'S THIS ABOUT YOU
TAKING SOME PERSONAL DAYS?

35:48.106 --> 35:48.977
YOU NEVER SAID ANYTHING.

35:48.977 --> 35:51.149
THAT'S WHY THEY'RE
CALLED "PERSONAL."

35:52.110 --> 35:54.193
[ SIGHS ]

35:54.193 --> 35:56.405
IT'S JUST A COUPLE DAYS
AT HOME.

35:56.405 --> 35:58.116
I'M...

35:58.116 --> 36:02.080
I HAVEN'T BEEN 100% LATELY.
I'M NOT SLEEPING.

36:04.623 --> 36:07.746
IT'S THAT GIRL,
ISN'T IT? THE FED?

36:07.746 --> 36:10.339
I WAS WONDERING WHY
I HADN'T SEEN HER AROUND.

36:10.339 --> 36:13.292
YEAH. SHE, UH -- SHE LEFT AFTER
THAT PARTY THE OTHER NIGHT.

36:13.292 --> 36:14.553
[ SIGHS ]

36:14.553 --> 36:16.215
GUESS SHE'D HAD ENOUGH
OF THIS PLACE.

36:16.215 --> 36:17.796
[ CHUCKLES ]
 WELL, I'M SORRY.

36:17.796 --> 36:19.218
AND IF IT'S ANY CONSOLATION,

36:19.218 --> 36:21.600
MY OLD MAN USED TO SAY
NEVER GET INVOLVED WITH A WOMAN

36:21.600 --> 36:23.512
WHO OWNS MORE HANDCUFFS
THAN YOU. SO...

36:23.512 --> 36:26.895
YEAH. [ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH, THAT'S --

36:26.895 --> 36:28.977
THAT'S ADVICE.

36:31.149 --> 36:32.901
SHE REALLY DID A NUMBER
ON YOU, DIDN'T SHE?

36:35.614 --> 36:37.946
YEAH.

36:37.946 --> 36:39.618
YEAH, I THINK SHE DID.

36:44.283 --> 36:48.667
Man: THE LORD IS MY SHEPHERD.
I SHALL NOT WANT.

36:48.667 --> 36:52.090
HE MAKETH ME TO LIE DOWN
IN GREEN PASTURES.

36:52.090 --> 36:55.043
HE LEADETH ME BESIDE
THE STILL WATERS.

36:55.043 --> 36:57.175
HE RESTORETH MY SOUL.

36:57.175 --> 37:00.008
HE LEADETH ME IN THE PATHS
OF RIGHTEOUSNESS

37:00.008 --> 37:01.430
FOR HIS NAME'S SAKE.

37:01.430 --> 37:05.183
YEA THOUGH I WALK THROUGH THE
VALLEY OF THE SHADOW OF DEATH,

37:05.183 --> 37:08.937
I SHALL FEAR NO EVIL,
FOR THOU ART WITH ME.

37:08.937 --> 37:12.521
THY ROD AND THY STAFF,
THEY COMFORT ME.

37:12.521 --> 37:16.945
THOU PREPAREST A TABLE BEFORE ME
IN THE PRESENCE OF MINE ENEMIES.

37:16.945 --> 37:19.528
THOU ANOINTEST MY HEAD WITH OIL.

37:20.319 --> 37:23.161
MY CUP RUNNETH OVER.

37:23.161 --> 37:24.663
OH, MY GOD!

37:26.535 --> 37:27.536
I'M DANIEL.

37:27.536 --> 37:29.167
I'M EMILY.

37:29.167 --> 37:30.789
WILL YOU MARRY ME?

37:32.170 --> 37:33.752
YES.

37:38.427 --> 37:39.878
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

37:44.303 --> 37:47.055
NO, DON'T -- DON'T --
DON'T DO IT.

37:47.055 --> 37:49.768
SORRY, PAL.
DAYLIGHT'S WASTING.

37:49.768 --> 37:50.979
OH, COME ON.

37:50.979 --> 37:54.393
WAKING UP WITH YOU
IS THE BEST PART OF MY DAY.

37:54.393 --> 37:57.025
IF YOU OPEN THOSE CURTAINS,
IT'S ALL OVER.

37:57.025 --> 37:59.358
COME ON. GIVE ME
A FEW MORE SECONDS HERE.

37:59.358 --> 38:02.991
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL GIVE YOU THREE.

38:02.991 --> 38:04.573
ONE, TWO...

38:04.573 --> 38:05.744
NO.

38:05.744 --> 38:06.785
...THREE.

38:11.289 --> 38:13.291
SURELY GOODNESS AND MERCY

38:13.291 --> 38:16.465
SHALL FOLLOW ME ALL THE DAYS
OF MY LIFE

38:16.465 --> 38:20.298
AND I WILL DWELL IN THE HOUSE
OF THE LORD FOREVER.

38:20.298 --> 38:22.090
AMEN.

38:22.090 --> 38:23.802
All: AMEN.

39:00.088 --> 39:01.720
[ BOTH SNIFFLE ]

39:04.222 --> 39:07.015
TAKE YOUR TIME.
I'LL BE HERE.

39:13.892 --> 39:16.184
[ SNIFFLES ]

39:23.692 --> 39:25.864
IT WAS A BEAUTIFUL
SERVICE.

39:28.366 --> 39:32.791
I FOUND THE ENVELOPE
YOU WERE LOOKING FOR.

39:32.791 --> 39:35.123
THANK YOU, LOUISE,
BUT I DON'T WANT IT.

39:36.545 --> 39:39.998
WOULD YOU DESTROY IT,
PLEASE?

39:39.998 --> 39:43.462
THAT WAY, WE CAN HOPE
FOR NO MORE FUNERALS.

39:51.219 --> 39:52.010
DAVID.

39:52.010 --> 39:54.062
I REALLY APOLOGIZE
FOR THE TIMING,

39:54.062 --> 39:56.685
BUT, UH, I THOUGHT
YOU WOULD WANT TO KNOW.

39:56.685 --> 40:00.108
MY GOOGLE ALERT HAS BEEN
BLOWING UP FOR THE LAST HOUR.

40:00.108 --> 40:01.279
BLOODBATH IN MIAMI.

40:01.279 --> 40:05.113
APPARENTLY AN UNIDENTIFIED
ARMS DEALER TURNED UP DEAD

40:05.113 --> 40:06.194
AND IN PIECES.

40:06.194 --> 40:07.986
IT'S KIND OF
REDUNDANT, HUH?

40:07.986 --> 40:10.619
WELL, I KNOW SOME PEOPLE THAT
ARE GONNA SLEEP WELL TONIGHT.

40:10.619 --> 40:11.409
UH-HUH.

40:30.679 --> 40:32.140
CHIEF ALVAREZ?

40:32.140 --> 40:33.181
YEAH.

40:33.181 --> 40:35.474
TED POWELL.

40:35.474 --> 40:36.815
HI.

40:36.815 --> 40:40.939
FBI BUREAU CHIEF --
LOWER MANHATTAN.

40:40.939 --> 40:44.062
ALL RIGHT.
SO, HOW CAN I HELP THE FBI?

40:44.062 --> 40:47.195
WELL, I'M TRYING TO TRACK DOWN
ONE OF OUR LOST SHEEP.

40:47.195 --> 40:48.777
SPECIAL AGENT KATE TAYLOR.

40:48.777 --> 40:50.909
SHE WAS DOING SOME
FIELD WORK.

40:50.909 --> 40:52.911
YEAH.
THE CONRAD GRAYSON MURDER.

40:52.911 --> 40:55.123
SURE. SHE WAS HERE,
CLOSED THE CASE,

40:55.123 --> 40:57.666
GOT CALLED BACK TO HER OFFICE
A FEW DAYS AGO.

40:59.167 --> 41:01.169
SHE NEVER MADE IT BACK.

41:01.169 --> 41:03.211
WAS SHE WORKING WITH
ANYONE ON YOUR TEAM?

41:03.211 --> 41:06.214
YEAH, ONE OF OUR ROOKIES,
UH, JACK PORTER.

41:06.214 --> 41:08.046
LET ME GIVE HIM A CALL.

41:08.046 --> 41:10.088
BUDGET CUTS ARE KILLING
YOU GUYS, TOO, HUH?

41:10.088 --> 41:11.299
HOW'S THAT?

41:11.299 --> 41:14.012
YOUR CAR.
NO GOVERNMENT TAGS.

41:16.855 --> 41:19.558
GOOD CATCH.

41:22.400 --> 41:24.983
IT'S ALWAYS THE LITTLE THINGS
THAT GET YOU.

41:24.983 --> 41:28.236
WHAT DID YOU SAY
YOUR NAME WAS AGAIN?

41:28.236 --> 41:29.487
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

41:29.487 --> 41:30.779
[ GROANS ]

41:31.489 --> 41:33.912
MALCOLM BLACK.

41:36.204 --> 41:39.377
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]
